td-067a70: Extensible Event Schema
Status: [open]
Type: epic | Priority: P2
Labels: extensible-event-schema

Description:
The audit log schema currently hardcodes HIPAA-specific fields, which creates unnecessary overhead for non-HIPAA tenants and leaves other framework-specific fields untyped in metadata. This change introduces universal core fields plus validated, namespaced framework extensions that remain queryable and deterministic for chain hashing.

Artifacts:
- Proposal: openspec/changes/extensible-event-schema/proposal.md
- Design: openspec/changes/extensible-event-schema/design.md
- Tasks: openspec/changes/extensible-event-schema/tasks.md
- Specs: openspec/changes/extensible-event-schema/specs/

