- Created `6` new `review-finding` issues.

**Critical**
1. `P1 bug` `td-350b22`  
Chain canonical payload still hashes legacy fields and omits `actor_id`/`extensions`, so extension tampering won’t affect checksum.  
Refs: [chain.ex:8](/Users/tbrewer/projects/goodway/goodaudit/app/lib/app/audit/chain.ex:8), [chain.ex:69](/Users/tbrewer/projects/goodway/goodaudit/app/lib/app/audit/chain.ex:69)

