Core validation still requires legacy `user_*` fields and framework modules still encode flat HIPAA-style requirements, conflicting with extensible schema goals.  
Refs: [log.ex:67](/Users/tbrewer/projects/goodway/goodaudit/app/lib/app/audit/log.ex:67), [hipaa.ex:5](/Users/tbrewer/projects/goodway/goodaudit/app/lib/app/compliance/frameworks/hipaa.ex:5)

